</ol>
<hr>
<div class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view Markdown-module__r02qCW__messageMarkdownHeading"><span class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view Text-module__KIh4Sq__text Text-module__KIh4Sq__multiline _sdz_text" style="--Text--font-family: inherit; --Text--font-size: var(--font-size-default); --Text--line-height: var(--line-height-default);"><strong>Langkah 3 — Copy file ke proyek (di Terminal Cursor)</strong></span></div>
<p>Tekan <code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">Ctrl+</code> ` (backtick) untuk buka terminal di Cursor, lalu:</p>
<div class="Markdown-module__r02qCW__agentWidePreBreakout"><pre><div class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__container"><div class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view _sdz_surface-bg _sdz_surface" style="--useView--pt: 8px; --useView--pr: 8px; --useView--pb: 8px; --useView--pl: 8px; --useView--border-radius: var(--border-radius-4);"><code class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__code" style="font-size: 14px; tab-size: 2; word-break: break-word; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: anywhere; cursor: text;"><div class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__line"><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span ͼ2f"># Buat folder yang belum ada</span></div><div class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__line"><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span ͼ36">mkdir</span><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span"> </span><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span ͼ2v">-p</span><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span"> src/components/mobile</span></div><div class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__line"><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span ͼ36">mkdir</span><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span"> </span><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span ͼ2v">-p</span><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span"> src/data</span></div><div class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__line"><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span ͼ36">mkdir</span><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span"> </span><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span ͼ2v">-p</span><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span"> src/hooks</span></div><div class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__line"><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span ͼ36">mkdir</span><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span"> </span><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span ͼ2v">-p</span><span class="CodeViewer2-module___Y4KcW__span cv2-span"> src/types</s