<p>Lalu <strong>drag &amp; drop</strong> file dari hasil download ke folder yang sesuai di Cursor:</p>
<div class="Markdown-module__r02qCW__agentWideTableBreakout"><table><thead><tr><th>File yang didownload</th><th>Taruh di sini</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">components/mobile/*.tsx</code></td><td><code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">src/components/mobile/</code></td></tr><tr><td><code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">data/waScripts.ts</code></td><td><code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">src/data/</code></td></tr><tr><td><code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">hooks/useStreak.ts</code></td><td><code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">src/hooks/</code></td></tr><tr><td><code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">types/mobile.ts</code></td><td><code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">src/types/</code></td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<hr>
<div class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view Markdown-module__r02qCW__messageMarkdownHeading"><span class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view Text-module__KIh4Sq__text Text-module__KIh4Sq__multiline _sdz_text" style="--Text--font-family: inherit; --Text--font-size: var(--font-size-default); --Text--line-height: var(--line-height-default);"><strong>Langkah 4 — Edit 1 file saja di Cursor</strong></span></div>
<p>Buka file <code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">src/app/page.tsx</code> (atau file dashboard utama kamu), cari bagian <code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">return (</code>, lalu minta Cursor AI untuk bantu:</p>
<p>Ketik di Cursor Chat:</p>
<blockquote>
<p><em>"Tambahkan MobileLayout di bawah desktop layout. Import dari @/components/mobile. Desktop pakai <code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">hidden md:block</code>, mobile pakai <code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">flex md:hidden h-screen</code>"</em></p>
