<hr>
<div class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view Markdown-module__r02qCW__messageMarkdownHeading"><span class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view Text-module__KIh4Sq__text Text-module__KIh4Sq__multiline _sdz_text" style="--Text--font-family: inherit; --Text--font-size: var(--font-size-default); --Text--line-height: var(--line-height-default);"><strong>Langkah 1 — Download dulu dari Replit</strong></span></div>
<p>Di Replit (browser sekarang), <strong>klik kanan folder</strong> <code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">artifacts/mobile-integration</code> → <strong>Download</strong><br>
→ Akan download file <code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">.zip</code> ke folder <code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">Downloads</code> Mac kamu</p>
<hr>
<div class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view Markdown-module__r02qCW__messageMarkdownHeading"><span class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view Text-module__KIh4Sq__text Text-module__KIh4Sq__multiline _sdz_text" style="--Text--font-family: inherit; --Text--font-size: var(--font-size-default); --Text--line-height: var(--line-height-default);"><strong>Langkah 2 — Buka terminal di Cursor</strong></span></div>
<p>Tekan: <strong><code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">Ctrl + backtick</code></strong> (tombol <code class="CodeRenderer2-module__jfz9nq__inline">`</code> di sebelah kiri angka 1)</p>
<hr>
<div class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view Markdown-module__r02qCW__messageMarkdownHeading"><span class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view Text-module__KIh4Sq__text Text-module__KIh4Sq__multiline _sdz_text" style="--Text--font-family: inherit; --Text--font-size: var(--font-size-default); --Text--line-height: var(--line-height-default);"><strong>Langkah 3 — Paste perintah ini satu per satu:</strong></span></div>
